itics</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Welsh_Anglicans" title="Category:Welsh Anglicans">Welsh Anglicans</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Welsh_occultists" title="Category:Welsh occultists">Welsh occultists</a></span> | <span dir='ltr'><a href="/wiki/Category:Decadent_literature" title="Category:Decadent literature">Decadent literature</a></span></div></div>			<!-- end content -->
